### Security Negative: Idempotency conflict (expect 409 on second)
@idemConflictUsers = users-create-conflict-001
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idemConflictUsers}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "username": "demo_conflict_a",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!",
  "displayName": "Demo A",
  "email": "demo_conflict_a@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "13800000003",
  "isActive": true,
  "roleIds": [],
  "departmentIds": []
}

### E2-02 准备：创建临时角色
# @name createTempRole
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "name": "即时生效测试角色",
  "code": "ROLE_EFFECTIVE_IMMEDIATE_DEMO",
  "description": "用于验证用户角色变更无需重新登录"
}

###
@tempRoleId = {{createTempRole.response.body.$.data.id}}

### E2-02 创建测试用户（绑定临时角色）
# @name createRoleEffectUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "username": "role.effect.user",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!2026",
  "displayName": "Role Effective User",
  "email": "role.effect.user@atlas.local",
  "phoneNumber": "13800000777",
  "isActive": true,
  "roleIds": [{{tempRoleId}}],
  "departmentIds": [],
  "positionIds": []
}

###
@roleEffectUserId = {{createRoleEffectUser.response.body.$.data.id}}

### E2-02 测试用户登录
# @name loginRoleEffectUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "role.effect.user",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!2026"
}

###
@roleEffectUserToken = {{loginRoleEffectUser.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### E2-02 变更前：测试用户查看 /auth/me（应看到临时角色）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{roleEffectUserToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### E2-02 管理员移除测试用户全部角色
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{roleEffectUserId}}/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "roleIds": []
}

### E2-02 变更后：同一旧 token 再访问 /auth/me（无需重新登录，角色应已变更）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{roleEffectUserToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idemConflictUsers}}
